THEY DON'T EVEN
HAVE THE WEAPON.

37:24.336 --> 37:27.036
DO THEY HAVE
A CREDIBLE EYEWITNESS?

37:27.102 --> 37:30.669
THEY DON'T HAVE
<i>ANY</i> EYEWITNESSES.

37:30.736 --> 37:32.202
WHERE'S THE CASE?

37:32.269 --> 37:36.636
HE DIDN'T SEEM UPSET
ENOUGH THE DAY AFTER
THAT HE WENT TO WORK?

37:36.702 --> 37:39.702
