38:19.202 --> 38:20.369
JEFFREY DID.

38:23.336 --> 38:24.836
JEFFREY DID...

38:28.036 --> 38:32.236
BECAUSE HE WAS UNDER OATH...

38:35.236 --> 38:41.369
