HE TOLD YOU ANOTHER TRUTH--

38:44.136 --> 38:49.236
HE DIDN'T KILL CINDY MARKS.

39:08.269 --> 39:09.436
[CLEARS THROAT]

39:12.536 --> 39:14.469
