POINTS TO A SURGEON.

39:14.536 --> 39:16.602
POSSIBLE IT WASN'T?
SURE...

39:16.669 --> 39:18.036
BUT LIKELY?

39:18.102 --> 39:21.236
THE EVIDENCE POINTS
TO CONSENSUAL SEX.

39:21.302 --> 39:24.802
POSSIBLE IT WAS RAPE
WITH NO BRUISING?
SURE...

39:24.869 --> 39:26.369
BUT LIKELY?

39:26.436 --> 39:29.969
THE EVIDENCE PROVES...
HE WAS THERE THAT NIGHT.

39:30.036 --> 39:34.169
POSSIBLE HE JUST
HAPPENED TO WALK IN
AFTER? SURE...

39:34.236 --> 39:35.569
BUT LIKELY?

39:35.636 --> 39:37.502
THE VICTIM WAS KILLED

39:37.569 --> 39:41.336
