SHOWED UP DEAD IN
HIS HOSPITAL

39:41.402 --> 39:44.669
WHERE HE GOT TO READ
THE AUTOPSY REPORT.

39:44.736 --> 39:49.536
POSSIBLE THAT'S JUST
A COINCIDENCE? SURE...

39:49.602 --> 39:51.602
BUT LIKELY?

39:51.669 --> 39:55.069
THEY'VE GOT A LOT
OF POSSIBILITIES,

39:55.136 --> 39:57.436
AND IN EACH AND
EVERY INSTANCE,

39:57.502 --> 40:01.469
THEY'RE ASKING YOU TO
ACCEPT THE MOST UNLIKELY
OF EXPLANATIONS.

40:01.536 --> 40:03.802
HOW'S THIS ONE?

40:03.869 --> 40:06.536
HE KNOWS THERE'S
A SERIAL KILLER

40:06.602 --> 40:09.269
WHO DECAPITATES
AND SEVERS HANDS,

40:09.336 --> 40:11.969
AND YET, ACCORDING
TO HIS TESTIMONY,

40:12.036 --> 40:13.969
WHEN HE WALKED IN
THAT ROOM

40:14.036 --> 40:17.436
AND SAW CINDY MARKS
DECAPITATED WITH
SEVERED HANDS,

40:17.502 --> 40:19.769
HIS VERY FIRST INSTINCT WAS,

40:19.836 --> 40:22.969
"OH, NO. THEY MIGHT
THINK I DID THIS."

40:23.036 --> 40:26.002
ISN'T THAT A LITTLE ODD?

40:26.069 --> 40:28.469
WOULDN'T
THE NATURAL REACTION BE,

40:28.536 --> 40:32.636
"IT'S OBVIOUS
WHO DID THIS.
IT'S THE POET"?

40:32.702 --> 40:36.769
AND WOULDN'T HE ASSUME
THE POLICE OFFICERS
WOULD SAY THE SAME?

40:36.836 --> 40:38.869
IS IT POSSIBLE
TO BELIEVE

40:38.936 --> 40:42.702
WHAT JEFFREY WINSLOW
IS TELLING YOU?

40:42.769 --> 40:46.836
SURE...BUT REMEMBER...

40:48.302 --> 40:54.569
HIS VERY OWN WIFE,
AS DEVOTED AS SHE WAS
ON THAT WITNESS CHAIR,

40:54.636 --> 40:56.502
SHE TOLD HER NEIGHBOR...

41:00.002 --> 41:02.369
"I think he did it."

41:49.136 --> 41:51.336
THE DEFENDANT
WILL PLEASE RISE.

41:57.236 --> 42:01.502
