READ US YOUR VERDICT.

42:03.969 --> 42:05.836
<i>"COMMONWEALTH</i>
<i>VERSUS WINSLOW.</i>

42:05.902 --> 42:09.569
"ON THE CHARGE OF MURDER
IN THE FIRST DEGREE...

42:09.636 --> 42:13.202
